title: Match of the Day - 20th September 2014 - HDTV X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Saturday 20th September 2014 
Time: 22:20 to 23:40 

Gary Lineker introduces highlights of the day's seven Premier League fixtures, including Liverpool's trip to West Ham. Last season the Reds beat a dogged Hammers side 2-1 in an incident-packed match at Upton Park during the title run-in. Two Steven Gerrard penalties ultimately proved the difference in a game that saw the woodwork struck on numerous occasions. Arsenal are also on the road, they travel to Aston Villa and have not been beaten by the West Midlands club at Villa Park since 1998, winning eight of those 14 contests. Elsewhere, Mark Hughes takes his Stoke side to former club QPR and Tottenham host West Bromwich Albion.

No spoilers please.
